# Day 27 Init: Building Tools and Plugins — Real Biological Data
# Sources:
#   FASTA sequences: NCBI RefSeq partial CDS for 10 human tumor suppressor / oncogenes
#   QC reads: Derived from real gene sequences with varied lengths for QC testing
#   Lib modules: Unchanged (define reusable functions)

mkdir("data")
mkdir("data/output")
mkdir("lib")
mkdir("tests")

# --- Real partial coding sequences from NCBI RefSeq ---
